  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "body": "Ryu's mother is an\u00a0${link_0}\u00a0citizen whose ${link_1} gained ${link_2} thanks to the ${link_3} of 171 ${link_4}. She is very loving, but also very exaggerated and clumsy, which causes Ryu embarrassment at times.",
